Class EventTypeList

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractCollection<TypeMirror>
java.util.AbstractList<TypeMirror>
org.microbean.event.EventTypeList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<TypeMirror>, Collection<TypeMirror>, List<TypeMirror>, SequencedCollection<TypeMirror>
public final class EventTypeList extends AbstractList<TypeMirror>
An immutable AbstractList of TypeMirrors that contains only legal event types, sorted in a specific manner.

Note: Two TypeMirror instances may represent the same type while not being equal to one another. List implementations such as this one that contain TypeMirror elements may also represent the same types without being equal to each other.

Author:
Laird Nelson
